data.description: Revel in the exquisite modern design featuring standard luxury upgrades! This residence boasts a prime location backing onto a freshwater canal, ensuring added privacy. Enjoy a comprehensive package, including a Full Kitchen Appliance Package, 16-Seer HVAC, Smart Thermostat, Smart Garage, and luxurious plank flooring throughout.    Indulge in the elegance of Quartz countertops in both the kitchen and bath, complemented by energy-efficient LED lighting. The open and spacious floor plan is enhanced by construction features designed for energy efficiency, such as Low-E double-pane windows, FOAM INSULATED CBS (concrete block) construction, and Spray Foam Insulation in the attic. Upgrade your lifestyle with this solar-powered home that not only enhances comfort but also contributes to substantial long-term savings!
